Step 1: Download JDK -> https://www.java.com/en/download/

step 2: Install JDK ->

step 3: Set the path of JDK -> C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.8.0_191\bin

This pc ->right click ->properties->advanced system settings
->environment variables->new ->path->PASTE YOUR PATH->click on OK

step 4: open your CMD
type java	

